{"_path":"/book/gimp","_dir":"book","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Gimp","description":"","director":"My","time":"2025","img":"gimp/1.png","plan":"100,100","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"book-content","props":{":by":"director",":img":"img",":plan":"plan",":title":"title"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"text-title","props":{":t":"为什么开始用 Gimp"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"随着 Adobe Photoshop 不断在联网上增加了很多限制，例如必须用 Adobe Creative Cloud  来进行安装。适用于 macOS 的破解版愈发稀少。虽然能用，但因为 macOS 系统更新的缘故。老版本越来越卡。如果是 Windows 10，我还可以继续用 PS cs6 版本，很轻量。再加上最近版本不断增加在线验证，即使能用，但半小时后、一小时后总会提示盗版弹窗，强制退出。（但断网是可以继续用的，不会弹窗）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"(可能 Adobe 会不断更新服务 API，即使 ban 了一个，几百个，也会继续增加新的，老是跟 Adobe 内耗也不是个办法。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"貌似这个弹窗只会针对 PS，单方面的给这个产品上强度，反之 Illustrator 和 After Effects 基本上没怎么弹过。个人还是很少用 Illustrator 的，更多用 Figma 替代他，AE 和 PS 倒是时不时会用上。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一直与 Adobe 这么耗下去也不是办法，经济实力还是消费不起。一个月要 167.51 HKD。毕竟我也不是艺术家，甚至很大一部分程度不是靠设计吃饭的，用 PS 最多的场景就是抠图，拆分、补补拆分后的素材。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因此我觉得这种小需求 GIMP 应该能满足我，顺便走出舒适圈，了解下新的环境。确实学到很多没有用的小知识。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"resynthesizer-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Resynthesizer 1"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"text-title","props":{"t":"Resynthesizer"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 PS 中有一个很好用的功能叫 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://helpx.adobe.com/cn/photoshop/using/content-aware-fill.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"”内容识别填充“"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，但在 GIMP 仅提供了 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.gimp.org/3.0/en/gimp-tool-heal.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Heal"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 有一说一还挺好用的，但是比较花时间？首先比较劝退的是 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.logarithmic.net/pfh/resynthesizer","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Resynthesizer"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。很难想象这么好的插件自 2004 起就已经发布，至今没有与预装在 GIMP 上。不过让我知道了 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ports.macports.org/port/gimp-resynthesizer/details/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"macports"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 有一说一没 Homebrew 好用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"于是我碰到了一个问题，GIMP 最新版本 3.0 无法使用 Resynthesizer，起码在 macOS 上，Windows 上貌似是可以的。于是需要自己编译，自己编译又会遇到 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/bootchk/resynthesizer/issues/154","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Run-time dependency gimp-3.0 found: NO"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/bootchk/resynthesizer/issues/144","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Fails to build, problem with i18n (fixed by making default build not generate i18n.) "}]},{"type":"text","value":" 这两个问题。让我体验到了类 Linux 的乐趣。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最终我选择了 GIMP 2.0 版本。但好像比 3.0 卡了许多？没 3.0 那么丝滑了，甚至比 PS 还略微的卡？可能是系统适配的缘故。兜兜转转一个小时已经很快过去，让我感受到了时间的流逝是如此之快。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"img-tip","props":{"text":"图 1 | 有一说一我觉得 PS 的操作是最舒服的，可以选择识别的范围，用绿色的进行涂抹。还是 <b>可视化的</b> 最终效果显然也是 PS 的最好","url":"gimp/test.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"或许未来有机会可以拿这个点子练练手，基于现在的这个加入类似 PS 的这种交互，应该会学到很多。不过一些复杂的还是会用 PS，一些简单的或许可以尝试下 GIMP，等我解决了这个问题在继续用 GIMP 弄一些复杂的好了。"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:book:gimp.md","_source":"content","_file":"book/gimp.